<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Action Not Allowed</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2, #fff);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 90%;
      padding: 28px 26px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #991b1b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #ef4444;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: background 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #dc2626;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">ðŸš«</div>
    <h1>Action Not Allowed</h1>
    <p>
      You are <strong>not the host</strong> of this room.<br />
      Only the host has permission to delete it.
    </p>
    <p class="note">
      Please ask the room host to delete the room on your behalf.
    </p>

    <a href="/room/setting/<%=userid%>"><button class="btn">Go Back</button></a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
